br />\n你係錯呀 錯在識錯女朋友 但要慶幸只係十個月而唔係十年<br />\n你仲有事業同屋企人要顧㗎<br />\n今晚好好休息 聽日就當新一頁開始啦！<br />\n<br />\n唔好飲太多喇 亦祝巴打你屋企人早日康復 同埋識返個好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242aad9a7b97f1f29ec2468fa9f0d0cf6be97833","tid":453992,"uid":122680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，明白你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我連酒都唔識飲，好辛苦...</blockquote><br />\n飲d甜d 易入口</blockquote><br />\n好想飲，想飲完好訓d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCocktail</blockquote><br />\n巴打，想問下，如果由你地出口講冷靜兩星期，其實係咪注定會結束呢段關係？</blockquote><br />\n如果佢無行動同結束無分別<br />\n好睇性格wo</blockquote><br />\n冷靜兩星期佢唔會搵我，但相信佢份人係會清楚咁處理段關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，亂入問其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c008f1eb7bfdf3f02c904ced772ad48a1149be16","tid":453992,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你值得更好呀巴打<br />\n<br />\n雖然上呢句廢話成日都會講 但我今日有追你post<br />\n你係錯呀 錯在識錯女朋友 但要慶幸只係十個月而唔係十年<br />\n你仲有事業同屋企人要顧㗎<br />\n今晚好好休息 聽日就當新一頁開始啦！<br />\n<br />\n唔好飲太多喇 亦祝巴打你屋企人早日康復 同埋識返個好女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前拍拖唔會咁樣<br />\n會付出 但自從初戀後唔敢付出更多<br />\n到今次我想改變自己<br />\n做返自己<br />\n但始終放唔下佢<br />\n你地局外人可能唔知道佢細路女姐<br />\n細路女做錯有幾奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961168b25c5f62a9a0f8668ae9bdeff3764accb2","tid":453992,"uid":141450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"你上個post唔係係咁鬧女朋友咩？"},{"pid":"3d5d399caff584e3eb6ab6bf3cb01af38fc106c8","tid":453992,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打，明白你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我連酒都唔識飲，好辛苦...</blockquote><br />\n飲d甜d 易入口</blockquote><br />\n好想飲，想飲完好訓d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCocktail</blockquote><br />\n巴打，想問下，如果由你地出口講冷靜兩星期，其實係咪注定會結束呢段關係？</blockquote><br />\n如果佢無行動同結束無分別<br />\n好睇性格wo</blockquote><br />\n冷靜兩星期佢唔會搵我，但相信佢份人係會清楚咁處理段關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，亂入問其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無所謂啦 變返毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗清楚前因後果啦<br />\n有人出師有名想冷淡變結束<br />\n亦有人係想靜下<br />\n局外人唔知咁多只會幫你亂下判斷<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊有信得過既人就一五一十講佢聽<br />\n比佢評下<br />\n或者最好方法 自己靜下來先 咁先判斷到<br />\n不過當局者迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce67e995c6040b3f96b4919704320acca863b810","tid":453992,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你上個post唔係係咁鬧女朋友咩？</blockquote><br />\n放唔底"},{"pid":"a43ee385836763971e8f66f8245fec0015d98cd1","tid":453992,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T17:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一切有從來就好<br />\n我都有錯 我以前好景個陣太輕手買野比佢<br />\n我都有份縱"}]}